Start or switch to Kodi:startkodi.sh
Stop Kodi:stopkodi.sh force
Restart Kodi:restartkodi.sh force
Install Kodi:confapps_ph.sh -p int -a Kodi
Uninstall Kodi:confapps_ph.sh -p rem -a Kodi
Update Kodi to the latest version (only if installed as a package):ph_update_pkg $PH_KODI_PKG_NAME
List all available options for Kodi:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a Kodi
View the current value of Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -g
View the current value of Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -g -r
Change the value of read-write Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -s
Change the value of read-write Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -s -r
Display help for Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -d
Display help for Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -d -r
Display TTY currently allocated to Kodi:confapps_ph.sh -p tty -a Kodi
Move Kodi to another TTY:confapps_ph.sh -p move -a Kodi -t prompt
XBOX360 controllers menu:ph_show_menu XBOX360
PS3 controllers menu:ph_show_menu PS3
PS4 controllers menu:ph_show_menu PS4
AppManagement menu:ph_show_menu AppManagement
Apps menu:ph_show_menu Apps
Controllers menu:ph_show_menu Controllers
Advanced menu:ph_show_menu Advanced
Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
Return to previous menu:return
